{title: Amazing Grace}
{artist: Traditional}
{key: G}
{capo: 0}
{copyright: Public Domain}

# Verse 1
{start_of_verse label="Verse 1"}
[G]Amazing [G7]grace, how [C]sweet the [G]sound
That [G]saved a [Em]wretch like [D]me
[G]I once was [G7]lost, but [C]now I'm [G]found
Was [G]blind, but [D]now I [G]see
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[G]Praise the [G7]Lord, praise [C]Him all ye [G]people
[G]Praise [Em]Him for His [D]mercy
[G]Praise the [G7]Lord, praise [C]Him all ye [G]people
[G]Praise [D]Him for ever[G]more
{end_of_chorus}

{textfont: Arial}
{chordsize: 12}
{new_page}
